text: Tinsel Korey (born March 25, 1980) is a Canadian actress. She is best known for playing Emily Young in the Twilight Saga movies New Moon and Eclipse. She played Jen in Tru Calling. She was born in Vancouver, British Columbia. ==References== Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Actors from Vancouver Category:1980 births Category:Living people
